<template>
    <ion-page>
        <ion-header>
            <ion-toolbar>
                <ion-title>Gérer mes séries de carte</ion-title>
            </ion-toolbar>
        </ion-header>
        <ion-content :fullscreen="true">
            <ion-header collapse="condense">
                <ion-toolbar>
                    <ion-title size="large">Tab 1</ion-title>
                </ion-toolbar>
            </ion-header>

            <ion-card class="ion-card-serie">
                <ion-card-header>
                    <ion-card-subtitle>Card Subtitle</ion-card-subtitle>
                    <ion-card-title>Card Title</ion-card-title>
                </ion-card-header>

                <ion-card-content>
                    Keep close to Nature's heart... and break clear away, once in awhile,
                    and climb a mountain or spend a week in the woods. Wash your spirit clean.
                </ion-card-content>
            </ion-card>

        </ion-content>
    </ion-page>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import { IonPage, IonHeader, IonToolbar, IonTitle, IonContent } from '@ionic/vue';

export default  {
    name: 'Tab1',
    components: { IonHeader, IonToolbar, IonTitle, IonContent, IonPage },
    data() {
        return {

            //Nos séries de cartes
            allSeries : null
        }
    },
    mounted() {
        
        axios.get("https://6060e5e2ac47190017a70428.mockapi.io/series")
            .then(response => {

                this.allSeries = response["data"];

            })
            .catch(error => {

                console.log(error);

            })
    }

}
</script>


<style scoped>

ion-content{
    position: relative;
    --ion-background-color : linear-gradient(348.02deg, #9C1176 6.53%, #F93C42 90.02%);
}

.ion-card-serie{
    margin-top: 20px;
    --ion-background-color : white;
}

</style>
